Oswestry.title: Oswestry
Oswestry.byline: Oswestry (Welsh: Croesoswallt) is a a market town and historic railway town in Shropshire, close to the Welsh border.

Oswego.title: Oswego
Oswego.byline: Oswego (population 17,000 in 2020) is a small city in Central New York on the southeastern shore of Lake Ontario at the mouth of the Oswego River.
